title: The New York Post: Lawmakers want news media to team up against Facebook, Google
text: Lawmakers in Congress are drafting a bill that would let news publishers team up against Facebook and Google.

title: Why Facebook Stock Is Headed Higher
text: Negative publicity on its handling of user-created content and privacy concerns is keeping a lid on the stock for now. Still, a rebound in economic activity could blow that lid right off.

title: 8 Top Tech Stocks Analysts Want You to Buy Now
text: 24/7 Wall St. reviews dozens of analyst research reports each day of the week with a goal of finding new ideas for investors and traders alike.
